<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      lang="en"
      metal:use-macro="context/main_template/macros/master"
      i18n:domain="iloactemp.backgroundnote">
<body>

<tal:comment tal:condition="nothing">
    This is a sample view template. It will not be used for rendering the
    content unless activated by creation of a view class with a matching name.
    
    Note that we're using Plone 4 macros. Replace them with Plone 3 macros
    if needed.
</tal:comment>

<metal:main fill-slot="content-core">
  <metal:content-core define-macro="content-core">

  <div>
  <h3></h3>
  <h1>A. ORGANIZATIONAL PROFILE</h1>
  <h3>1. Basic organizational information</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/organization_information/output"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/organization_comment"></p>
  <h3>2. Source of regulation</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/regulation_source/output"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/regulation_comment"></p>
  <h3>3. Membership</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/membership/output"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/membership_comment"></p>
  <h3>4. Structure</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/structure/output"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/structure_comment"></p>
  <h3>5. Involvement in the ILO governance and supervisory structures</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/involvement_ilo/output"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/involvement_ilo_comment"></p>
  <h3>6. Involvement in the other international bodies</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/involvement_other/output"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/involvement_other_comment"></p>
  </div>



  <div>
  <h1>B. POLICY ENVIRONMENT AND PRIORITIES </h1>
  <h3>1. Overview of country context</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/overview_country/output"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/overview_country_comment"></p>
  <h3>2. Overview of the overall national business agenda</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/overview_business/output"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/overview_business_comment"></p>
  <h3>3. Key policy priorities of the EO</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/key_policies/output"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/key_policies_comment"></p>
  <h3>4. Policy dialogue modalities</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/policy_dialogue/output"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/policy_dialogue_comment"></p>
  <h3>5. Key policy documents/Sources of information and documentation</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/key_documents/output"></p>
  </div>


  <div>
  <h1>C. ORGANIZATIONAL ANALYSIS</h1>
  <h3>1. Vision, objectives and mission statement</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/vision/output"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/vision_comment"></p>
  <h3>2. Assessment of membership</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/assessment_membership/output"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/assessment_membership_comment"></p>
  <h3>3. Direct services</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/direct_services/output"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/direct_services_comment"></p>
  <h3>4. Advocacy services</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/advocacy_services/output"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/advocy_services_comment"></p>
  <h3>5. Income</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/income/output"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/income_comment"></p>
  <h3>6. Relations with the government and trade unions</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/relations"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/relations_comment"></p>
  </div>


  <div>
  <h1>D. RELATIONS WITH ILO, UN, MULTILATERAL AND BILATERAL DEVELOPMENT
      COOPERATION AGENCIES</h1>
  <h3>1. Engagement in the DWCP</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/engagement_dwcp/output"></p>
  <h3>2. Views on ILO policy in particular field</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/"></p>
  <h3>3. Major results achieved with the ILO support in the last biennium</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/"></p>
  <h3>4. ILO projects the EO  is involved in</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/"></p>
  <h3>5. Summary of any other international assistance/funding provided by
      donor governments or bilateral development cooperation agencies</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/"></p>
  <h3>6. Recent ACT/EMP activities</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/"></p>
  <h3>7. Involvement in ILO ITC training</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/"></p>
  <h3>8. Involvement in the UNDAF development and implementation</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/"></p>
  </div>



  <div>
  <h1>E. ACTEMP STRATEGY</h1>
  <h3>1. Organizational needs analysis/baseline situation</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/"></p>
  <h3>2. Current major issues or objectives that need to be addressed in the EO
  <p tal:content="structure context/"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/"></p>
  and how do these issues or objectives align with the EOâ€™s
  organizational/strategic plans</h3>
  <h3>3. Results intended to be achieved by ACTEMP</h3>
  <p tal:content="structure context/"></p>
  <p tal:content="context/"></p>
  </div>


  </metal:content-core>
</metal:main>

</body>
</html>

